{"type":"text","timestamp":1773436099223,"sessionID":"ses_316fcc12bffeSBLLi3jBrbT2M4","part":{"id":"prt_ce90745790010QKt7s6i90Q5c9","sessionID":"ses_316fcc12bffeSBLLi3jBrbT2M4","messageID":"msg_ce9073e960010E73YHHLumdy5C","type":"text","text":"I see — `\"PT0S\"` is a string with length > 0, so it enters the first branch. It parses to 0 minutes (not `Infinity`), so no warning is emitted from the first branch. The `else if` never triggers because the first condition was true. So my test expectation was wrong — PT0S does NOT produce a \"No effort estimate\" warning. Let me fix the test:","time":{"start":1773436099223,"end":1773436099223}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773436102234,"sessionID":"ses_316fcc12bffeSBLLi3jBrbT2M4","part":{"id":"prt_ce9074efe0017UODBsQhaEendr","sessionID":"ses_316fcc12bffeSBLLi3jBrbT2M4","messageID":"msg_ce9073e960010E73YHHLumdy5C","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_012pAccvBTpmJXijAbMz2C9S","tool":"edit","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-unit-test-suite/tests/task-schema.test.ts","newString":"  test(\"does not warn for PT0S effort (parseable but zero)\", () => {\n    // PT0S is a valid ISO 8601 duration that parses to 0 minutes.\n    // The \"No effort estimate\" branch only triggers when effort is falsy.\n    const issues = validateTask(makeValidTask({ effort: \"PT0S\" }));\n    const warnings = warningMessages(issues);\n    expect(warnings.filter((m) => m.includes(\"effort\"))).toHaveLength(0);\n  });","oldString":"  test(\"reports warning for PT0S effort\", () => {\n    const issues = validateTask(makeValidTask({ effort: \"PT0S\" }));\n    const warnings = warningMessages(issues);\n    expect(warnings.some((m) => m.includes(\"No effort estimate\"))).toBe(true);\n  });"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","title":"tests/task-schema.test.ts","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-unit-test-suite/src/lib/worktree.ts":[],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-unit-test-suite/src/index.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":585,"character":10},"end":{"line":585,"character":16}},"message":"Unreachable code detected.","severity":4,"code":7027,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":605,"character":8},"end":{"line":605,"character":14}},"message":"Unreachable code detected.","severity":4,"code":7027,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":635,"character":6},"end":{"line":635,"character":12}},"message":"Unreachable code detected.","severity":4,"code":7027,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":728,"character":8},"end":{"line":728,"character":14}},"message":"Unreachable code detected.","